547
01:04:25,470 --> 01:04:28,347
Well, l'll tell you the truth.
l didn't really forget to turn the sign on.

548
01:04:28,431 --> 01:04:31,684
Just doesn't seem
like any use any more, you know.

549
01:04:32,686 --> 01:04:35,563
See, that used to be
the main highway right there.

550
01:04:35,647 --> 01:04:36,897
Well, wanna come in and register?

551
01:04:36,982 --> 01:04:38,440
No, no, sit down. l don't wanna trouble you.

552
01:04:38,525 --> 01:04:41,735
-l just wanna ask a few questions.
-No, that's no trouble. Today's linen day.

553
01:04:41,820 --> 01:04:44,405
l always change the beds here once a week
whether they've been used or not.

554
01:04:44,489 --> 01:04:46,907
Hate the smell of dampness, don't you?
lt's such a...

555
01:04:46,992 --> 01:04:49,743
l don't know, creepy smell. Come on.

556
01:04:51,037 --> 01:04:52,997
You out to buy a motel?

557
01:04:54,666 --> 01:04:55,833
No.

558
01:04:56,334 --> 01:04:57,835
Reason l ask, you said you'd seen so many

559
01:04:57,919 --> 01:05:01,088
in the past couple of days,
l thought maybe you...

560
01:05:01,172 --> 01:05:03,799
What... What was it you wanted to ask?

561
01:05:03,883 --> 01:05:06,677
Well, you see,
l'm looking for a missing person.

562
01:05:06,761 --> 01:05:10,014
My name's Arbogast.
l'm a private investigator.

563
01:05:10,098 --> 01:05:11,932
l've been trying to trace a girl

564
01:05:12,017 --> 01:05:15,769
that's been missing for, oh,
about a week now from Phoenix.

565
01:05:15,854 --> 01:05:18,397
lt's a private matter.
The family wants to forgive her.

566
01:05:18,481 --> 01:05:20,608
She's not in any trouble.

567
01:05:21,067 --> 01:05:23,861
l didn't think the police went looking
for people who aren't in trouble.

568
01:05:23,945 --> 01:05:26,071
-l'm not the police.
-Oh, yeah.

569
01:05:26,156 --> 01:05:27,990
We have reason to believe
that she came along this way.

570
01:05:28,074 --> 01:05:30,534
May have stopped in the area.
Did she stop here?

571
01:05:30,619 --> 01:05:33,203
Well, no one's stopped here
for a couple of weeks.

572
01:05:33,288 --> 01:05:35,623
Would you mind looking at the picture
before committing yourself?

573
01:05:35,707 --> 01:05:36,957
Commit myself?

574
01:05:37,042 --> 01:05:40,919
-You sure talk like a policeman.
-Look at the picture, please.

575
01:05:41,588 --> 01:05:42,630
Mmm-mmm.

576
01:05:42,714 --> 01:05:44,423
-Sure?
-Yeah.

577
01:05:45,342 --> 01:05:47,635
Well, she may have used an alias.

578
01:05:47,719 --> 01:05:49,178
Marion Crane's her real name,

579
